Devour		KEY:Devour ~ Xtabay		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialAttack.Extraordinary	DEFINE:DevourSaveDC|10+CON		DESC:While a creature is under the effects of a xtabay's soporific pollen, the plant may, as a full-round action, occupy the same square as the sleeping creature and slowly sap the life from it.  Every round the xtabay uses this ability, the creature must make DC %1 Fortitude save or take 1d2 Con damage.  This feeding is curiously painless, and normally isn't enough to waken a foe put to sleep by the plant.  Each round this feeding continues, the sleeping victim can attempt a new DC %1 Will save to awaken.|DevourSaveDC		BONUS:VAR|DevourSaveDC|2|PREFEAT:1,Ability Focus (Devour)				SOURCEPAGE:p.289

Soporific Pollen	KEY:Soporific Pollen ~ Xtabay	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialAttack.Extraordinary	DEFINE:SoporificPollenSaveDC|10+CON	DESC:As a standard action, a xtabay can release sleep-inducing pollen into the air around it.  Each creature within a 10-ft.-radius burst centered on the xtabay must make a DC %1 Will save or fall asleep for 1d3 minutes.  A creature that succeeds on the Fortitude save cannot be affected by the same xtabay's soporific pollen for 24 hours.  A creature put to sleep by this pollen can be awakened by vigorously shaking the sleeper (a standard action) or by damaging it.  This is a mind-affecting sleep effect.|SoporificPollenSaveDC	BONUS:VAR|SoporificPollenSaveDC|2|PREFEAT:1,Ability Focus (Soporific Pollen)	SOURCEPAGE:p.289

Acid Sting		KEY:Acid Sting ~ Xtabay		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialAttack.Extraordinary							DESC:A xtabay's sting does an additional 1d2 acid damage.																																																																																													SOURCEPAGE:p.289	ASPECT:Ability Benefit|(1d2)

###Block: Yrthak Abilities
